Json to add recipe(Create method):
{
        "recipeName": "Pulao",
        "recipeType": "VEG",
        "noOfServings": 1,
        "ingredients": "Rice, Vegetables, Water",
        "instructions": "Saute the vegetables and add masala. Add water and semi-cooked rice.Cook for 10 minutes. "
}

Json to update recipe(Put method):
{
    "recipeType": "NON_VEG"
}

Json to implement Search functionality:
{
    "recipeType": "VEG",
    "noOfServings": 2,
    "ingredientInclude": false,
    "ingredients": "pasta",
    "instructionInclude":true,
    "instructions": "bowl"
}